source.name: Watts per MIPS - Ray Kurzweil
source.dataPublishedBy: Ray Kurzweil (2005, updated to 2015). The Singularity Is Near: When Humans Transcend Biology.
source.additionalInfo: Computing efficiency is measured as the number of watts used per computation/operation per second. Here it is measured in Watts per MIPS (Millions of instructions per second).
